description:
We asked 50 a16z partners: What big ideas in tech will define 2025?

An external "AI brain." Big swings in biopharma. Infinite games. A
nuclear resurgence. "Faceless" creators. Google search challengers.
Battlefield AI. 

These are just a few of the big ideas we think will shape innovation in 2025 and beyond. 

Check out the full list of ideas: https://a16z.com/big-ideas-in-tech-2025/
